EnronOnline Management Report for June please find the Daily EnronOnline Executive Summary Special Announcement This report can now be accessed directly through the EnronOnline Intranet Site at In order to access this report click on the link above Once there follow the link entitled Reports and then select the Secured Reports tab A dropdown menu will appear with a list of the various secured reports available for viewing After choosing the report you are interested in a security window will appear requiring you to enter your Windows login ID and password Simply enter your standard login and the report will load automatically We look forward to your feedback and comments If you have any questions or experience any difficulties accessing your reports through the Intranet Site please feel free to contact either Bryan Deluca at x or Simone La Rose at x Embedded Picture Metafile
